          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "By authors.  The main advantage of using a 4PI summing",
                "detector is that the response of the NaI(Tl) crystal",
                "leads predominantly to a single peak, called sum peak,",
                "at the sum of the energies of the cascading",
                "transitions."
              ]
            }
